Comparison of observed and predicted values
The model performance is compared with observed and predicted values for all cultivars across experiment Gatton2015. The plots below show the observed vs predicted values for different traits. Each point represents an observation from an experiment. The closer the points are to the diagonal line, the better the performance of the model for that trait.
The range of observed and predicted values are estimated using data in this page, which may be misleading for the narrow ranges of observed and predicted values.
